# Design Tokens

All visual properties in `packages/dbt-tools/web/` must use design tokens from [`tokens.css`](mdc:packages/dbt-tools/web/src/styles/tokens.css).

## Quick reference

| Category | Token pattern | Example |
|----------|--------------|---------|
| Background | `--bg-*` | `var(--bg-canvas)`, `var(--bg-surface)`, `var(--bg-elevated)` |
| Text | `--text-primary`, `--text-secondary`, `--text-tertiary` | `var(--text-primary)` |
| Border | `--border-*` | `var(--border-subtle)`, `var(--border-default)` |
| Icon | `--icon-*` | `var(--icon-primary)`, `var(--icon-accent)` |
| Accent | `--accent-*` | `var(--accent-primary)`, `var(--accent-hover)` |
| Status | `--text-success`, `--text-danger`, `--text-warning`, `--text-info` | |
| Chart | `--chart-1` through `--chart-8` | |
| dbt type | `--dbt-type-{model,source,test,...}` and `--dbt-type-*-soft` | |
| Graph | `--graph-*` | `var(--graph-panel)`, `var(--graph-text)` |
| Spacing | `--space-{0,0.5,1,1.5,2,...,16}` | `var(--space-3)` = 0.75rem |
| Font size | `--text-{2xs,xs,sm,md,base,lg,xl,2xl}` | `var(--text-sm)` = 0.8125rem |
| Display | `--text-display-{sm,md,lg}` | Fluid `clamp()` for hero text |
| Line height | `--leading-{none,tight,snug,normal,relaxed,loose}` | |
| Font family | `--font-sans`, `--font-display`, `--font-mono` | |
| Radius | `--radius-{sm,md,lg}` | |

## Rules

- **CSS**: Always use `var(--token)` for colors, spacing, typography, and radii. Never hardcode hex, rgb, rem, or px for these properties. Stylelint (`declaration-strict-value`) enforces this for colors and radii.
- **TypeScript** (canvas/SVG): Import from `constants/themeColors.generated.ts`. Never edit that file manually — run `pnpm tokens:sync`.
- **New tokens**: Add to both `:root` and `[data-theme="dark"]` in [`tokens.css`](mdc:packages/dbt-tools/web/src/styles/tokens.css), then run `pnpm tokens:sync`.
- **Legacy aliases** (`--text`, `--bg`, `--panel`, `--mint`, `--rose`, `--amber`): Do **not** use in new code. Use the semantic name from the table above.
- **Class names**: BEM kebab-case (`block__element--modifier`).
- **Verify CSS changes**: Run `pnpm lint:stylelint` (not covered by `lint:report`).

Full detail: [AGENTS.md](mdc:AGENTS.md), [`styles/README.md`](mdc:packages/dbt-tools/web/src/styles/README.md).
